     750                          ;               (TIMER VALUES INTL,INTH; # BITS INBITS; INOUT=FF; 
     751                          ;               IN ROUTINE VECTOR INPORT; RDYMSK; INSTAR START MASK) 
     752                          ;               RETURNS THROUGH STREST, WITH APPROP ERROR RETURNS, 
     753                          ;               FRAME AND NOT READY 
