    1988                          ;       .BYTE   'SZ' 
    1989                          ; 
    1990                          ; 
    1991                          ; ABOVE FILLER ADJUSTS FOR CONTROLLER (THIS), HANDLER, AND 
    1992                          ; RELOCATOR SIZE TO FILL THE FINAL ROM.  FINAL MEMORY MAP LOOKS 
    1993                          ; LIKE THIS: 
    1994                          ; 
    1995                          ; ($F000) - (RELOCR-1)          CONTROLLER (THIS) UP TO HERE 
    1996                          ; (RELOCR) - (RELOCR+5)         DISK IMITATION SECTOR 0 FLAGS 
    1997                          ; (BOOTB+6) - (BOOTE-2)         CODE PART OF RELOCATOR (SENT IN 
    1998                          ;                               ONE PIECE AFTER POLL, OR SENT AS 
    1999                          ;                               THREE DISK BLOCKS IMITATION DISK; 
    2000                          ;                               LATTER CASE CHECKSUMS AT DISKCH) 
    2001                          ; (RELCHK)                      RELOCATOR CHECKSUM 
    2002                          ; (HANDLB) - (HANDLE-2)         CODE PART OF HANDLER 
    2003                          ; (HNDCHK)                      HANDLER CHECKSUM 
    2004                          ; ($FFF9)                       ROM VERSION NUMBER 
    2005                          ; ($FFFA) - ($FFFB)             ROM CHECKSUM 
    2006                          ; ($FFFC) - ($FFFD)             RESET VECTOR 
    2007                          ; ($FFFE) - ($FFFF)             IRQ (BRK) VECTOR 
    2008                          ; 
    2009                          ; FINAL ASSEMBLY PROCEEDS AS FOLLOWS: 
    2010                          ;   SET BOOTB, BOOTE PER HANDLER AND RELOCATOR CODE SIZES 
    2011                          ;          (DON'T FORGET CHECKSUMS) 
    2012                          ;   ADJUST FILLER 
    2013                          ;   USING CHECKSUM PROGRAM, CALCULATE RELOCATOR CHECKSUM 
    2014                          ;   USING CHECKSUM PROGRAM, CALCULATE DISKCH AND HNDCHK SUMS 
    2015                          ;          (NOTE THAT THIRD DISKCH SUM COVERS STUFF FOLLOWING 
    2016                          ;           RELOCATOR) 
    2017                          ;   SET VERSION NUMBER 
    2018                          ;   SET CHECKSUM AT END OF POLL ANSWER (BEFORE POLLE) 
    2019                          ;   REASSEMBLE 
    2020                          ;   CALCULATE ROM CHECKSUM AND REASSEMBLE 
    2021                          ;   UPLOAD RESULT 
    2022                          ; 
    2023                          ; 
    2024                                  *=      RELOCR 
