    2026  F913  00 05                     .WORD   $0500           ; ENTRY ADDRESS 
    2027  F915  C0 E4                     .WORD   $E4C0           ; ADDRESS OF RTS INSTRUCTION IN OS !!!!!
    2028                          ; 
